    RESOURCE_USING_XNAME_TITLE "x:Name is used instead of x:Key."
    RESOURCE_USING_XNAME_IMPACT 
                            "Setting x:Name creates a backing field that consumes memory and CPU time."
    RESOURCE_USING_XNAME_SOLUTION "Have a property on the ViewModel that retrieves the resource from the ResourceDictionary only when needed."
    RESOURCE_USING_XNAME_DESCRIPTION "x:Name set on Resource %1 of type %2."
    RESOURCE_USING_XNAME_LINK_TITLE "More information about this rule."
