    NON_VIRTUALIZED_ITEMS_PANEL_TITLE "Element with ItemsSource set is using non-virtualizing panel."
    NON_VIRTUALIZED_ITEMS_PANEL_IMPACT 
                            "A non-virtualized ItemsControl will increase load time and resource usage by loading more of its child items than necessary."
    NON_VIRTUALIZED_ITEMS_PANEL_SOLUTION "Use either ItemsStackPanel or ItemsWrapGrid for your ItemsPanel instead of %1."
